amendment.description: An amendment numbered 9 printed in Part B of House Report 118-535 to prohibit funds from being used to ban or remove the photograph "V-J Day in Times Square.".

vote.text: On agreeing to the Burchett amendment (A005) Agreed to by voice vote.

action.text: House amendment agreed to: On agreeing to the Burchett amendment (A005) Agreed to by voice vote.
